article.description: — Taurus Samuels had a career-high 23 points as Dartmouth beat Georgetown 69-60 on Saturday.
article.headline: Samuels scores 23 to carry Dartmouth past Georgetown 69-60
article.linkText: Samuels scores 23 to carry Dartmouth past Georgetown 69-60
article.story: WASHINGTON -- — Taurus Samuels had a career-high 23 points as Dartmouth beat Georgetown 69-60 on Saturday. Brendan Barry had 19 points and eight rebounds for Dartmouth (1-1). Ryan Cornish added 14 points. Aaryn Rai had six assists. Aminu Mohammed had 17 points and six rebounds for the Hoyas (0-1).
